    "\"My platoon leader provides me with emotional support,\" and \"My platoon leader shows genuine concern for my behavioral health\") on a 5-response Likert-type scale (1 = Strongly Disagree, 5 = Strongly Agree; alphas =.90T1 and.94T2).",
